Privacy Policy

At Mihir Raghani, we are committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality of our clients' personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information provided to us during the course of providing graphic design services.

1. Information Collection

We may collect personal information, such as names, contact details, billing information, and project-related details necessary to deliver our graphic design services. This information is collected through communication channels such as emails, phone calls, and online forms.

2. Use of Information

Personal information collected is used solely for the purpose of delivering and improving our graphic design services. This includes project management, communication with clients, invoicing, and providing updates on project progress.

3. Information Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer clients' personal information to third parties without explicit consent, except as required by law or to fulfill services requested by the client (e.g., working with printing partners to fulfill print design projects).

4. Data Security

We employ industry-standard security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of clients' personal information. This includes secure data storage, encryption, and limited access to sensitive information.

5. Cookies and Analytics

Our website may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance user experience and collect non-personal information for analytical purposes. Users can manage cookie preferences through their browser settings.

6. Third-Party Links

Our website or communications may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites and encourage users to review their respective privacy policies.

7. Consent

By using our graphic design services or providing personal information, clients consent to the collection, use, and processing of their information as described in this Privacy Policy.

8. Access and Updates

Clients have the right to access, update, or request deletion of their personal information held by us. Requests for such actions can be made by contacting us using the provided contact details.

9. Changes to the Policy

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and clients will be informed of significant updates.

Contact Information

For any inquiries or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact Mihir Raghani at +91 9427629611.
